description:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Business Support Officer&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;KFM Band 5&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Managed Services&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;KFM are looking for an enthusiastic and capable individual to join our team to provide Executive Assistant support to the Director of Managed Services and Business Support to the Managed Services Leadership Team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Using your skills and knowledge, alongside your relevant professional experience you will be responsible for supporting the Managed Service Leadership team to continue to develop and deliver our services, systems and processes. You will work closely with both our internal and external stakeholders to ensure the Senior Management team can work efficiently and effectively.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will have a proven track record is supporting senior management teams, taking own initiative and being creative in establishing and maintaining office systems and processes to continually improve ways of working.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our Managed Services team pride themselves on taking a special interest in staff growth and development and you will be supportive of this.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Please note:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please note our timescales for recruitment are as follows;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Anticipated Closing Date: 13th November 2020&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Shortlisting Outcomes: 18th November 2020&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Interview Date: 26th November 2020&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We have the right to close the advert prior to the closing date of this advert, so to avoid disappointment early applications are highly advisable.&lt;/p&gt;
